text: Chamseddine Harrag (; born 10 August 1992) is an Algerian footballer who plays for MC Alger in the Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1. == References == Category:Living people Category:1992 births Category:Algerian footballers Category:USM El Harrach players Category:NA Hussein Dey players Category:MC Alger players Category:Association football midfielders
